OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FA prison officer was left with a
OL,7,Fsevered artery in his neck while
OL,8,Fanother received a punctured lung
OL,9,Ffollowing the attack by Manchester
OL,10,FArena bomb plotter Hashem Abedi, it
OL,11,Fhas been revealed.
OL,13,FAbedi, 28, the brother of the
OL,14,FManchester Arena bomber, Salman Abedi,
OL,15,Fis also said to have hoarded sachets
OL,16,Fof butter, which he then melted and
OL,17,Fthew over a female prison officer,
OL,18,Fleaving her with third degree burns.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
