OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FThe Prison Officer's Association (POA)
OL,7,Fsaid the attack involved homemade
OL,8,Fweapons, with injuries inflicted to
OL,9,Fboth male officers "potentially fatal".
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer says
OL,12,Fhe is "appalled" by the attack, with
OL,13,Fthe government will urgently
OL,14,Finvestigating what happened, his
OL,15,Fofficial spokesman has said.
OL,17,FCounter-terrorism police have since
OL,18,Ftaken over the investigation into
OL,19,FAbedi's actions at HMP Frankland in
OL,20,FCounty Durham, on Saturday 12 April.
OL,26,@tD@GOUtD@PO]
