OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice also says it
OL,7,Fwill carry out a review following the
OL,8,Fattack, and has suspended access to
OL,9,Fkitchens in separation and close
OL,10,Fsupervision units, where inmates are
OL,11,Fkept apart from the general prison
OL,12,Fpopulation.
OL,14,FThe full extent of what happened has
OL,15,Fbeen revealed by Mark Fairhurst, the
OL,16,FNational Chairman of the Prison
OL,17,FOfficers Association.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
