OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FHe told The Guardian that Abedi had
OL,7,Fproduced two homemade knives, adding:
OL,8,F"We think that he's made knives out of
OL,9,Fa baking tray from that kitchen area.
OL,11,F"One (officer) had a severed artery,
OL,12,Fwas stabbed in the neck, and one's got
OL,13,Fsevere stab wounds in the back,
OL,14,Fincluding a punctured lung," Fairhurst
OL,15,Fsaid, adding that the officers also
OL,16,Freceived third-degree burns.
