OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FAbedi was convicted of assisting with
OL,7,Fthe Manchester Arena terror plot, in
OL,8,Fwhich his suicide bomber brother
OL,9,FSalman Abedi killed 22 people by
OL,10,Fdetonating a homemade rucksack-bomb in
OL,11,Fa crowd of concert-goers.
OL,13,FThe attack took place in a separation
OL,14,Fcentre at HMP Frankland, which houses
OL,15,Fless than 10 prisoners and is where
OL,16,Fthose considered to be the most
OL,17,Fdangerous and extremist are held.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
