OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FMr Fairhurst added: "I'm absolutely
OL,7,Ffurious that terrorist prisoners, who
OL,8,Fpose such a significant risk to
OL,9,Fnational security, are allowed the
OL,10,Fsame freedoms and privileges as
OL,11,Fprisoners on normal location.
OL,13,F"We should not be allowing prisoners
OL,14,Fin separation centres to access
OL,15,Fcooking facilities, so they have the
OL,16,Fresources and implements that can
OL,17,Finflict violence on staff.
OL,26,@nD@UOU
