OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,F"There's only one way to reduce the
OL,7,Frisk and prevent this ever happening
OL,8,Fagain, and to reduce the risk, you
OL,9,Fhave to stop prisoners' access to
OL,10,Fkitchens, because we're worried about
OL,11,Fcopycat incidents.
OL,13,F"They get prison food, they get three
OL,14,Fmeals a day. Why do they need to cook?"
OL,16,FHe said more investment was needed
OL,17,Ffrom the Treasury in order to improve
OL,18,Fconditions for prison staff.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@gO]
