OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,F"This just highlights how violent our
OL,7,Fworkplace is, that your life is on the
OL,8,Fline every single shift - every single
OL,9,Ftime you go on duty you're subject to
OL,10,Fthreats, abuse and violence, every
OL,11,Fsingle day, and let's be honest, we
OL,12,Fhaven't got the adequate protections
OL,13,Fin place," he said.
OL,15,F"We deal with exactly the same
OL,16,Fincidents as police officers, exactly
OL,17,Fthe same violence, the same
OL,18,Fhostilities, yet we don't have the
OL,19,Fsame protections. We don't even have
OL,20,Fstab-proof vests."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@JO]wD@AOU|D@RO]
