OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FSpeaking of the attack, the prime
OL,7,Fminister's spokesman said: "The Prime
OL,8,FMinister is appalled by the attack
OL,9,Fthat we saw at the weekend and his
OL,10,Fthoughts are with the officers
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"Prison staff work around the clock to
OL,14,Fkeep the country safe and we will
OL,15,Fnever tolerate the violence that is
OL,16,Ftargeted towards them.
OL,26,@oD@\OUuD@AOU
