OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,F"It's clear that something went
OL,7,Fterribly wrong in the management of
OL,8,Fthis offender and the Government is
OL,9,Fcommitted to carrying out an
OL,10,Finvestigation to urgently get answers."
OL,12,FHe went on: "Offenders should be
OL,13,Fmanaged in such a way that our prison
OL,14,Fofficers are kept safe and there will
OL,15,Fbe an investigation here into what
OL,16,Fhappened that allowed this incident to
OL,17,Fhappen."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]tD@MOUyD@HO]
