OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FAbedi was previously found guilty
OL,7,Falong with two other convicted
OL,8,Fterrorists, of attacking a prison
OL,9,Fofficer at southeast London's Belmarsh
OL,10,Fprison in 2020.
OL,12,FMr Fairhurst said the union was
OL,13,Frequesting an urgent meeting with the
OL,14,Fjustice secretary, Shabana Mahmood,
OL,15,F"to discuss what happened and put our
OL,16,Fcase forward to issue prison officers
OL,17,Fon the frontline stab-proof vests".
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@bO]
