OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FHe said that pending the review,
OL,7,Faccess to prison kitchens "should be
OL,8,Fremoved immediately, and it should
OL,9,Fnever be allowed again".
OL,11,FMr Fairhurst also said the promised
OL,12,Freview of the incident should be
OL,13,Fcarried out independently.
OL,15,F"If they're serious about improving
OL,16,Fconditions for staff and clamping down
OL,17,Fon violence then they will commission
OL,18,Fthat independent review," he said.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@WO]wD@AOUzD@YO]
