OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,F"We don't want it kept in-house, we
OL,7,Fwant an independent expert on terror
OL,8,Fto look at what went wrong and make
OL,9,Frecommendations."
OL,11,FThe MoJ has not yet said who will
OL,12,Fcarry out the review, or whether
OL,13,Fcooking facilities for prisoners will
OL,14,Fbe suspended in the interim.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
