OL,3,CPrison officers 'stabbed in back and
OL,4,Cneck' in Abedi attack
OL,6,FAn MoJ spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts remain with the two prison
OL,8,Fofficers still in hospital as they
OL,9,Frecover. There will be a full review
OL,10,Finto how this attack was able to
OL,11,Fhappen, alongside the separate police
OL,12,Finquiry. The government will do
OL,13,Fwhatever it takes to keep our
OL,14,Fhardworking staff safe."
OL,16,FCategory A is the highest level of
OL,17,Fsecurity and Frankland has housed
OL,18,Fother notorious inmates, including
OL,19,FFusilier Lee Rigby's terrorist killer
OL,20,FMichael Adebolajo, Yorkshire Ripper
OL,21,FPeter Sutcliffe, and Charles Bronson.
